doctype
html
	head
		title OAuth Classroom Server - Not for Production Use
	body
		h1 (This page was generated by the OAuth Server)
		p
			|An application with the client id 
			=clientId
			|  is asking for access to your todo lists.
		p Do you want to grant this application access to your todo list data?		
		form(action='/grant' method='post')
			select(name='allow')
				option grant
				option deny			
			input(type='hidden' name='oauth2_redirect' value=redirect)
			input(type='hidden' name='oauth2_clientId' value=clientId)
			input(type='hidden' name='oauth2_state' value=state)
			button(type='submit') Submit